00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:31,600
[Legend of Fuyao]

21
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:34,900
~ Episode 61 ~

22
00:01:56,900 --> 00:02:00,000
Your Highness, where are we going now?

23
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,300
Go back.

24
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:09,820
What?

25
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:11,600
Go back to the Imperial City.

26
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:16,400
If we rush back to the Imperial City now, then that's walking right into the trap.

27
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:20,600
Could it be that Your Highness still has some other plans?

28
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,300
Plan?

29
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:27,300
This is my last plan.

30
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:31,100
I've long secretly taken notes of the configuration of Zhangsun Jia's army.

31
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,340
If he isn't reliable,

32
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:38,200
this then will be my last life-saving straw.

33
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,900
Your Highness is wise.

34
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:49,100
If a person doesn't know to leave himself grounds for retreat,

35
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:52,700
then that's forcing oneself to walk a doomed path!

36
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:56,700
When we return to the Imperial City,

37
00:02:56,700 --> 00:03:01,300
Your Highness can tell His Majesty that just for the empire,

38
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:03,700
you bore the humiliation and sided with the enemy so that you could investigate their military situation.

39
00:03:03,700 --> 00:03:08,200
Your Highness is, after all, His Majesty's own flesh and blood.

40
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,900
His Majesty will be lenient.

41
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,400
Yes!

42
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:17,400
No matter how my Emperor Father will punish me,

43
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:21,600
as long as I'm alive, that's way better than anything!

44
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:24,810
Right?

45
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,240
Xu Lai,

46
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:35,990
do you know what I have done wrong?

47
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:43,600
My mistake is getting born in this imperial family, be this unfavored son,

48
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:46,300
and being unable to resign to my fate!

49
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:55,600
Your Highness, don't blame me.

50
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,200
You can only blame the unfairness of this world.

51
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:02,000
I've followed you for such a long time and just wanted to have a good future.

52
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,800
You have now lost your power.

53
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:07,600
I have to find myself a way to survive, right?

54
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,430
Prince Virtue said that we wouldn't be able to depend on you sooner or later.

55
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,600
If you escape, I must kill you.

56
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:16,200
For a person like me, I never had any principles.

57
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:19,800
I only care about who's stand I'm taking and not who's right or wrong.

58
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:23,900
You were the one who taught me all this.

59
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,270
Young Lord, it's already about 1:00 a.m.

60
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:07,170
You should rest.

61
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,770
Tell me.

62
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:14,390
If these chess pieces had thoughts,

63
00:05:15,170 --> 00:05:17,440
what would they be thinking?

64
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:24,180
The world is like a game of chess.

65
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:32,600
Although we're not chess pieces, we'll hold ourselves back involuntarily because we are unwilling to be manipulated.

66
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:36,800
After a long time, we'll forget the principle that even if we keep calculating our wins and losses,

67
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:39,800
we won't be able to escape this small area.

68
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:50,500
Who really is this person that you're talking about?

69
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:53,000
Who do you think?

70
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,600
It can't be the person that I'm thinking...

71
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,200
But in doing this,

72
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:17,960
what is his purpose exactly?

73
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:22,160
It's for? Who is he targeting?

74
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,800
Is it Prince Virtue?

75
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,000
Or you?

76
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:29,800
Could... Could it be Wuji?

77
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,800
You are quite clever.

78
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,130
This?

79
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,400
I don't understand.

80
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:46,100
Of course, you wouldn't understand.

81
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:51,800
All of these can only be explained by the past.

82
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:57,280
That year, I was just 16,

83
00:06:58,170 --> 00:07:03,600
but in my heart, I was already deeply in love with a certain person.

84
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:08,760
We wanted to be together for a lifetime.

85
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:15,000
When he was preparing to go to my house and ask for my hand in marriage,

86
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:21,800
the newly crowned Lord Emperor announced that he wanted to marry me.

87
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,200
I didn't want to get married.

88
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,300
I wanted to escape.

89
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:31,560
But behind us, there were a lot of loved ones.

90
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:39,010
In the end, I hesitated.

91
00:07:40,150 --> 00:07:42,420
He gave up.

92
00:07:44,290 --> 00:07:48,190
But only when I married into the palace did I know

93
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:53,350
that the emperor who married me didn't really care about me.

94
00:07:54,860 --> 00:08:01,330
Everything he did was just to separate us.

95
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:08,700
If it's not doing it for Wuji,

96
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:14,600
for him to be able to become the emperor one day,

97
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:19,100
I would have long given up on all these things and just went away with him.

98
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:23,400
As long as one can be with the person she loves,

99
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:34,200
those gossiping mouths and a chaotic world wouldn't really mean a thing.

100
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:42,000
Do you want to leave?

101
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:48,980
Want to live paradise-like days with him?

102
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:52,600
Your ideas are possible, too.

103
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,900
But Empress,

104
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:58,800
you always like to mix reality with imagination.

105
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:04,400
In this world, how can there be so much romanticism and sweetness?

106
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,800
Informing Prince.

107
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,200
Was your injury grave?

108
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,200
I was incompetent.

109
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,200
Did you get any information?

110
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:29,400
Empress indeed got abducted by His Majesty.

111
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:32,000
Is it that our plan got leaked in advance?

112
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,200
Yes.

113
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,150
I risked my life to return and inform you.

114
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:37,800
I fear that the other palace spies are already—

115
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:41,600
Do you know where she's being locked up right now?

116
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,900
His Majesty did this matter in a very covert manner.

117
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:46,800
I wasn't able to find it out in the palace.

118
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,700
Leave and get your wounds treated.

119
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:55,420
I wasn't able to fulfill your order.

120
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:58,400
I deserve to die! May Prince punish me.

121
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,000
It's fine.

122
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:03,050
This wasn't your fault, either.

123
00:10:03,050 --> 00:10:04,890
Go now.

124
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:15,200
Prince, the reinforcements that Crown Prince mobilized have arrived through the southern mountain pass.

125
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:19,400
Roughly estimating it, there are more than 300,000 of them.

126
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:22,800
Also, they seemed to be trying to surround us.

127
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,700
Our plan—

128
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:29,800
Spread my order, we'll go to battle tomorrow.

129
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:34,800
When they see the smoke signal, let General Ma set out to war.

130
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,600
What about our arrangements in the palace?

131
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:41,000
I still have to carefully think about it.

132
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,600
Leave now.

133
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,000
Yes.

134
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,400
Leave now.

135
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:20,240
I'll send men to escort you.

136
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,220
Nothing bad will happen to you.

137
00:11:26,100 --> 00:11:29,430
In the past, it's me who was unfaithful to you.

138
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:35,400
If there are sins, mistakes, or retributions, they should all be paid by me.

139
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:41,760
It's me who didn't take good care of you two.

140
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:47,970
In the future, I fear that I won't have any chance to make up for it anymore.

141
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:53,110
The only thing I can do now is to let you go,

142
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:57,100
let you live well.

143
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:05,580
Why don't you ask for the reason that I took Lian'er and left without a word back then?

144
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:08,650
Where have I been hiding all these years?

145
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:11,190
How did I live my days?

146
00:12:17,100 --> 00:12:19,630
I was disloyal to you at that time.

147
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,140
You should hate me.

148
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:29,940
I didn't search for you two then, not because I was heartless,

149
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,600
but because staying farther away from me

150
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:36,410
might allow you two to live better.

151
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:42,000
Live better?

152
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:46,680
You totally don't know what happened that time.

153
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:55,100
What really do you want to do?

154
00:12:58,100 --> 00:13:02,940
Try guessing where Wuji's army is now.

155
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:07,460
No...

156
00:13:07,460 --> 00:13:09,220
Wuji is the Crown Prince of Megrez!

157
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:11,130
He's your son! You!

158
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:13,450
You shouldn't treat him like this!

159
00:13:13,450 --> 00:13:15,060
You're going to harm Wuji?

160
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:18,260
Isn't it enough that you take Zhangsun Jia's and my lives?

161
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:21,000
Why must you still involve Wuji in this?

162
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,490
What mistake has he done?

163
00:13:23,490 --> 00:13:25,400
Wuji respected you so much!

164
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,500
You actually want to use him to seek revenge?

165
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:30,490
You all think that I'm using others,

166
00:13:30,490 --> 00:13:36,230
but have you ever realized that the whole Megrez is also using me?

167
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:42,200
The Lord Emperor may look like he has power over the whole world, but that's not actually the case.

168
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:45,480
He's being restricted by the Five Regions, being exhausted by millions of citizens.

169
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,680
You all have seen that.

170
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:56,340
We still have time today.

171
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:03,790
In here, I'll tell you two a story.

172
00:14:03,790 --> 00:14:05,930
Maybe after today,

173
00:14:05,930 --> 00:14:10,770
no one will know about the origin of this matter anymore.

174
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:18,980
Once, there was a pair of brothers born from the same mother and grew up together.

175
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:22,780
It can be said that they had deep affection for each other.

176
00:14:22,780 --> 00:14:27,830
The little brother was intelligent and quick-witted, easily earning the doting of people.

177
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:35,870
Everyone would love him a bit more.

178
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:41,510
And this older brother was young but lacked vigor and drive, was not eloquent.

179
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:50,550
His father treated this character of his as being mediocre and dull.

180
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:53,550
He wasn't good at explaining,

181
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:57,360
so he just focused on studying hard

182
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,920
from early in the morning to late at night;

183
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:02,660
hoping that one day,

184
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:07,290
he could unburden his parents of some responsibilities.

185
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,450
You have guessed it, right?

186
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:14,510
The younger brother is Zhangsun Jia.

187
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:21,620
And that older brother who their father assumed to be dull is me.

188
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:26,490
Afterwards,

189
00:15:26,490 --> 00:15:32,230
my Emperor Father never hid his favoritism of Zhangsun Jia.

190
00:15:32,230 --> 00:15:36,930
Everyone in the whole empire knew it.

191
00:15:36,930 --> 00:15:39,450
After conferring me as the Crown Prince,

192
00:15:39,450 --> 00:15:45,920
the voices of people wanting to remove me and make Zhangsun Jia as the Crown Prince never stopped,

193
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:50,210
but my Emperor Father never did so.

194
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:56,080
Fuyao, do you know why?

195
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:04,750
Maybe... because your Emperor Father still cared about you.

196
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:09,470
That's also what I initially thought.

197
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:13,350
The emperor position of our Megrez is really an ominous one.

198
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:17,010
For the past three or four emperors, not one was able to live beyond forty years old.

199
00:16:17,010 --> 00:16:21,240
With His Majesty suddenly collapsing from sickness now, it must be an unlucky sign.

200
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:25,440
To tell you the truth, based on His Majesty's appearance earlier, he probably will just last for three to five days.

201
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:29,910
Even if they are able to come up with a method to save him, I fear that it's already too late.

202
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:32,990
But we must preserve our life.

203
00:16:32,990 --> 00:16:34,290
Of course.

204
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:35,980
I heard that someone just died in the palace today.

205
00:16:35,980 --> 00:16:37,460
What's that about?

206
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:40,020
Someone wanted to suggest making Second Prince as the crown prince.

207
00:16:40,020 --> 00:16:42,770
This angered His Majesty so much that he ordered his execution right there and then.

208
00:16:42,770 --> 00:16:45,320
But hasn't His Majesty always favored Second Prince?

209
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:50,200
Since he loves him so dearly, how can he bear to let him suffer that evil curse of the royal throne?

210
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,240
That's right, too.

211
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:55,970
Before, I heard His Majesty told Her Ladyship that this Second Prince is his favorite.

212
00:16:55,970 --> 00:16:58,620
He surely won't let him unfairly die just for the Five Regions.

213
00:16:58,620 --> 00:17:00,790
So, they were talking about this?

214
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:02,740
Yes. Think about it.

215
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:05,750
If he becomes the emperor, he'll only be able to live up to thirty plus years.

216
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:09,100
But isn't this being too unfair to Crown Prince?

217
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:15,650
But afterwards, I learned that Emperor Father clearly knew

218
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:20,950
that the emperor throne of Megrez is a deadlock that no one can break.

219
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:28,060
And I was just a chess piece in his hand that he pushed into that throne.

220
00:17:28,060 --> 00:17:33,180
In the end, I am a sacrificial offering to the throne of Megrez Empire!

221
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:35,570
A sacrificial offering!

222
00:17:35,570 --> 00:17:39,760
Since you knew it yourself, why didn't you make a choice?

223
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:42,120
You still couldn't let go of that supreme power.

224
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:44,280
Of course, I've thought about it.

225
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:49,660
I realized that even if I won't get a good death while on this throne,

226
00:17:49,660 --> 00:17:52,120
but other than the life of myself,

227
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:54,450
I will be able to control the life and death of everyone!

228
00:17:54,450 --> 00:17:58,060
Yours, hers, the life and death of all of you!

229
00:17:58,060 --> 00:17:59,620
Your Majesty,

230
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:05,450
but after all, you are still on that throne for so many years.

231
00:18:05,450 --> 00:18:08,120
It's enough to prove that those short life rumors were false.

232
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,060
Those rumors are not false.

233
00:18:10,060 --> 00:18:16,950
This deadlock was broken by using several decades of my time to suffer pain for a lifetime as an exchange.

234
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:19,430
But so what?

235
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:25,650
The descendants of Zhangsun can now forever be rid of this curse.

236
00:18:25,650 --> 00:18:29,060
In my Megrez imperial throne,

237
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:31,680
the heir can now live for a very long time,

238
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:35,270
so all this pain is nothing.

239
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:39,470
Your Majesty, since that's the case, why then must you—

240
00:18:39,470 --> 00:18:42,560
Because someone betrayed me!

241
00:18:43,700 --> 00:18:49,790
Not only a betrayal, she caused an emperor to suffer humiliation!

242
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:04,740
So... you've known it all along?

243
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:18,570
Empress... I want you to tell it to me personally.

244
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:23,640
Whose son is Wuji?

245
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,300
It's...

246
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:37,900
Wuji is...

247
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,390
Wuji is—

248
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:54,090
For all these years,

249
00:19:54,090 --> 00:20:00,230
have you always thought that it was because I discovered your affair with Empress,

250
00:20:00,230 --> 00:20:04,520
I took Lian'er and left in a rage?

251
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:08,130
I indeed believed so.

252
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:14,040
Yes.

253
00:20:15,390 --> 00:20:21,010
The peach flower blossomed so beautifully that year.

254
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:27,150
