257
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:38,940
Even more, we wouldn't have lost our way inside the palace

258
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:41,000
and heard things that we shouldn't have heard.

259
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:49,060
