That day, I learned about the greatest secret of the imperial palace.

274
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:53,490
I was so afraid.

275
00:21:53,490 --> 00:21:55,040
I...

276
00:21:57,970 --> 00:22:01,530
I was afraid...

277
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:06,370
I took Lian'er and tried to escape for our lives and

278
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:08,820
