287
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:34,970
She never saves people out of pity.

288
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:37,570
One has to pay a price.

289
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:39,190
What price?

290
00:23:39,190 --> 00:23:41,900
