303
00:24:53,860 --> 00:24:56,200
I won't inappropriately ask for your forgiveness.

304
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:59,910
But for the situations in the past, sometimes, I was left with no choice.

305
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:02,230
