307
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:11,930
It was you.

308
00:25:11,930 --> 00:25:13,600
It was you who killed Lian'er.

309
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:16,610
It was you who created all of this mess!

310
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:23,910
I hate you! I hate you!

311
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:31,520
